WEBVTT

00:10:57.082 --> 00:11:00.784
whereas the newcomers,
they were so not used to feeling this way

00:11:00.808 --> 00:11:02.860
that they were now even more depressed.

00:11:02.884 --> 00:11:03.979
(Laughter)

00:11:04.003 --> 00:11:08.841
So you could see writers
from Bangladesh or Turkey or Egypt

00:11:08.865 --> 00:11:12.295
trying to console their colleagues

00:11:12.319 --> 00:11:16.778
from Brexit Britain
or from post-election USA.

00:11:16.802 --> 00:11:18.441
(Laughter)

00:11:19.230 --> 00:11:20.477
But joking aside,

00:11:20.501 --> 00:11:24.898
I think our world is full
of unprecedented challenges,

00:11:24.922 --> 00:11:27.960
and this comes with an emotional backlash,

00:11:27.984 --> 00:11:30.205
because in the face of high-speed change,